snippet.title: Rad Venture - SAGE 2020 DEMO Gameplay
snippet.description:
This is a gameplay trailer for our SAGE 2020 Demo for Rad Venture!
This is an early alpha version of Rad Venture and some things are subject to change.

Check out our Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/knickknackgames

Please follow our social media accounts for update:
-Knick-Knack Games Website: http://knickknackgames.com/
-Rad Venture Twitter: https://twitter.com/Rad_Venture
-Knick-Knack Games Twitter: https://twitter.com/Knickknackgames
